column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_r,p.devrad_r,p.devraderr_r,  s.specobjid, s.veldisp, s.z, s.veldisperr,s.specobjid, g.specobjid, g.lgm_tot_p1#, g.lgm_tot_p8#, g.lgm_tot_p5# FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid join galSpecExtra as g on g.specobjid =s.specobjid WHERE  class = &&& and  s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND zWarning=#
